The Atom Publishing Protocol
2007", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC5023.html", target="_top", tooltip="The Atom Publishing Protocol (AtomPub) is an application-level protocol for publishing and editing Web resources.  The protocol is based on HTTP transfer of Atom-formatted representations.  The Atom format is documented in the Atom Syndication Format. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
